fields.title: Harry Potter
fields.author: J.K. Rowling
fields.description: The "Harry Potter" series is a globally popular fantasy book series written by J.K. Rowling, consisting of seven books, published between 1997 and 2007. It follows the journey of Harry Potter, a young wizard, as he discovers his magical heritage, attends Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry, and battles the dark wizard Lord Voldemort, who seeks immortality and domination over the wizarding and non-magical (Muggle) worlds.

fields.title: Hobbit
fields.author: J.R.R. Tolkien
fields.description: "The Hobbit" is a fantasy novel written by J.R.R. Tolkien, first published in 1937. It serves as a prequel to The Lord of the Rings and follows the adventure of Bilbo Baggins, a comfort-loving hobbit who is unexpectedly swept into an epic quest.

fields.title: The Alchemist
fields.author: Paulo Coelho
fields.description: A young shepherd named Santiago embarks on a journey to find a hidden treasure, learning about destiny and personal legend along the way.

fields.title: Atomic Habits
fields.author: James Clear
fields.description: A practical guide on how small habits can lead to remarkable changes in life and career.
